Package org.mozilla.javascript.arrays

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExternalArray
    The abstract base class for the different types of external arrays.
    ExternalByteArray
    An implementation of the external array using an array of bytes.
    ExternalClampedByteArray
    An implementation of the external array using an array of bytes.
    ExternalDoubleArray
    An implementation of the external array using an array of "double"s.
    ExternalFloatArray
    An implementation of the external array using an array of "float"s.
    ExternalIntArray
    An implementation of the external array using an array of "int"s.
    ExternalShortArray
    An implementation of the external array using an array of "short"s.
    ExternalUnsignedByteArray
    An implementation of the external array using an array of bytes.
    ExternalUnsignedIntArray
    An implementation of the external array using an array of "int"s.
    ExternalUnsignedShortArray
    An implementation of the external array using an array of "short"s.
